        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                "8 PIECE PISTOL CLEANING KIT – The ASR Outdoor pistol cleaning kit comes with everything you’ll need to keep your pistol clean and ensure optimal performance – 2 bronze brushes, 2 wool brushes, 2 brass rods, a plastic handle, and microfiber absorbent patches.",
                "MULTI-CALIBER COMPATIBILITY – This pistol cleaning kit is suitable for .357, 38 and 9mm pistols.  With this kit, you’ll be able to keep your pistols clean and ready for your next trip to the range.",
                "COMPACT DESIGN – The kit comes with a durable plastic carry case that measures just 5” x 3.5” and weighs .25lbs (4oz) so it will easily fit inside most range bags. All of the pieces fit inside, ensuring that your gun cleaning tools stay organized when not in use.",
                "2 TYPES OF BRUSHES – Our kit comes with 2 different types of gun cleaning brushes – phosphor bronze and wool. Bronze brushes are great for a superior clean, and wool brushes can easily sweep out loose carbon.",
                "ABSORBENT PATCHES – The kit comes with microfiber absorbent patches to help absorb dust and debris, and they are great for applying cleaning solvents without damaging your pistol."
            ],
